I left 8 minas 10 shekels of silver with Bélia and Dudaya to make purchases with; Bélia owes 22 minas of copper
Alabum son of Sú-Dibar owes 1 mina of silver and 23 minas of fine copper, Puzur-Ana son of Gatum being guarantor; he will pay within 3 weeks, if he doesn't pay, he will add (interest) according to the rule of the kârum
Assur-bél-awatim son of Su-Anim owes 3 minas of silver, he will add (interest) according to the rule of the kârum; furthermore: 1 talent of fine copper
